OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FStarting fine and dry with
OL,6,Flittle cloud and light winds. By the
OL,7,Fafternoon some patchy cloud will
OL,8,Fdevelop, and there is a low risk of
OL,9,Fisolated showers in the afternoon.
OL,10,FSome brisk easterly winds developing,
OL,11,Ffeeling cooler along the coast.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FDry, with cloud building
OL,14,Fthrough the evening. Some low cloud
OL,15,Fmay spread in from the coast later on
OL,16,Fwith hill fog possible overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
