OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FAny low cloud quickly
OL,6,Fdissipating to leave another dry day
OL,7,Fwith good spells of sunshine. Feeling
OL,8,Fnoticeably cooler in the brisk
OL,9,Feasterly breeze.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,12,FShowers possible on Thursday evening
OL,13,Fwith temperatures increasing again.
OL,14,FMostly dry on Friday with variable
OL,15,Fcloud and sunny intervals. Cloudy on
OL,16,FSaturday with a risk of showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
